---
title: Paneer Veggie Curry (V) with Sweet Potato and Courgette
description: What’s not to love about this recipe? The Paneer veggie curry embodies all the great flavours of India. The Paneer cheese melts beautifully into a sauce with base flavours of Garam Masala and Turmeric. Finish it off by sprinkling over some Almond flakes and then get ready to take a trip through some great Indian flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/paneer-veggie-curry-adf08ddd-fde6b505.jpg
